quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  27,14,"Ɓe yeddi [Aayeeje ɗen], tawi wonkiiji maɓɓe ɗin no yananaa fii majje, tooñe e mawnintinaare. Ndaaru ko honno laatornoo battane fennuɓe ɓen"
  27,15,"Gomɗii Men okkii Daawuuda e Sulaymaana Ganndal ɓe maaki: \"Yettoore nden woodanii Alla On ɓurnuɗo men e dow ɗuuɗuɓe immorde e jeyaaɓe Makko gomɗinɓe ɓen"
  27,16,"Sulaymaana roni Daawuuda, O maaki: \"Ko onon yo yimɓe, men anndinaama haala colli ɗin, men okkaama immorde e kala huunde, Pellet, ɗumɗoo ko ɗum woni ɓural ɓanngungal"
  27,17,"Sulaymaana mooɓanaa koneeli makko ɗin immorde ka jinnaaji e ka yimɓe e ka colli, kamɓe ko ɓe yuɓɓinaaɓe"
  27,18,"Haa nde ɓe arunoo e aynde korndolli ɗin, korndolil wi'i: \"Ko onon yo korndolli, naatee ka koɗanɗi mooɗon, fii wata Sulaymaana e koneeli mu'un ɗin muncu on, hara kamɓe ɓe so'aa"
  27,19,"[Sulaymaana] moosi ko o jaluɗo immorde e konngol maggi ngol, o maaki: \"Jooma, lonnginam no mi yettira neema maaɗa mo neeminɗaa e dow am on, e jibibinɓe lam ɓen, e nde mi gollata ko moƴƴi weltoraa ɗum, naadaami ka Yurmeende Maaɗa wonndude e jeyaaɓe Maaɗa moƴƴuɓe ɓen"
  27,20,"O ƴewtii colli ɗin, o maaki: \"Ko heɓi lam, mi yi'aali Hud-huda. Kaa ndu laati jeyaandu e wirniiɗi ɗin"
  27,21,"Maa mi lepta ndu sanne lepte saɗtuɗe maaɗum maa mi hirsandu sanne, maaɗum ndu addana lam hujja ɓannguɗo"
  27,22,"Ndu ñiiɓe ko woɗɗaa, ndu wi'i: \"Mi huɓindike ko a huɓindaaki ɗum, mi addanii ma immorde to Saba'i kumpital yananaangal"